data.description: Generously sized 6 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home located on 1.2 acres in Shepherd!  Featuring a large kitchen with lots of cabinets, island, snack bar and walk-in pantry. Split floorplan for privacy. Spacious primary bathroom consists of double vanity, linen closet, separate shower, corner tub, tile flooring, and large walk-in closet. Fenced back yard with privacy fence & chain link. Covered patio, concrete driveway, & large beautiful oak trees.
